Interface ListenerRegistration

    public interface ListenerRegistration
extends AnnotableRegistration
    Current registration status of a Listener instance. The current registration status is obtained from the underlying listener.

        boolean equals(@Nullable
             java.lang.Object o)
        Compares the specified object with this listener registration for equality. Returns true if the specified object is also a listener registration and the two registrations have the same listener implementation class. This definition ensures that this method works properly across different implementations of the listener registration interface.
